The paper deals with the synthesis of time-lapse videos using deep neural networks, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) and conditional generation, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with the correlation between illumination change and time of day, which is a topic related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
